                    tokenType,
                    balance,
                    tokenId || null
                ]
            );

            logger.info(`Directly updated token balance for ${address} and token ${tokenAddress} to ${balance}`);
        } catch (error) {
            logger.error(`Error updating token balance for ${address} and token ${tokenAddress}:`, error);
            throw error;
        }
    }
